gation and AllowAdd must contain the sort field. The other sections must be configured that either the HideNavigationPanel = true or AllowAdd/AllowDelete = false. \n \n   Related articles \n \n \n Page: \n  Panel (00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000) has default sort set to column Name. This column does not exist in the panel. Cannot set default sort.  \n \n \n Page: \n  Panel\u2019s data source has no primary key. Cannot render panel.  \n \n \n Page: \n  Error occurred while loading role list  \n \n \n Page: \n  Can\u2019t save model because it crashes on memory error (System.OutOfMemoryException)","vector_provider":"AI.Ollama.OllamaTextEmbeddingGenerator","vector_generator":"__","last_update":"2026-04-29T00:23:54"},"vector":[-0.038722273,-0.0074481308,-0.074462496,0.026802886,-0.025051024,0.0005227445,0.0036365287,0.024049355,0.001363189,-0.00546332,0.01809589,-0.0064158533,-0.039366864,0.032951284,-0.015352321,-0.0017519632,0.02113318,0.011178491,0.023772802,0.020092687,-0.0036283517,-0.0015782248,0.028189426,0.033594027,-0.027466493,0.03688413,-0.0723265,-0.026328783,-0.024095213,-0.011436315,-0.013773001,-0.012250052,0.038318858,-0.016889,-0.025901197,-0.0041465894,-0.029691119,-0.03328317,-0.023271028,0.0062033106,-0.04257374,0.047022764,0.0050642085,-0.019474106,-0.017409869,-0.023649443,-0.014393795,-0.007088279,0.054938212,-0.018415954,-0.012211188,-0.06335786,0.028908521,-0.03427455,-0.012717966,0.020741988,-0.019308398,-0.029846262,0.008467004,0.0034962266,-0.0020311873,-0.03154642,-0.006355957,0.008072592,0.0384885,0.009863176,0.021619864,-0.006230237,-0.009025098,-0.036732063,0.023811305,0.024060188,-0.06840967,-0.014717698,-0.07741945,0.013744411,-0.00074781425,0.00751422,-0.021839594,-0.01103604,0.02400466,-0.018023353,0.0018168659,-0.03048819,0.0005517735,0.04409149,-0.013025807,0.074841574,0.026669804,0.026312776,-0.03388185,0.0024339713,0.04977557,-0.034103442,-0.040008865,-0.022438908,0.0066265464,-0.015996104,0.025098968,-0.013285761,0.019612374